b'\n\n\n\n\nBenedict Allen\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n NEW: get the full picture with Benedict Allen on Instagram!\n\n\n\n\n\n\nYoutube\nTwitter\nFacebook\nShop\n\n\n\xa0AboutNewsPublic SpeakerGalleryContact\n\n\n\n\n\nImmersion in\xa0\xa0other worlds...\nAuthor, environmentalist, film-maker, international motivational speaker.\nBenedict Allen became established as one of the world\'s leading modern-day explorers through expeditions famously achieved not with a phone, GPS or "backup," but by preparation alone with remote indigenous communities. Dispensing with a film crew, he went on to pioneer the authentic recording of adventurous journeys for TV.\n\n\n\n\n\n\nUpcoming events\n26th February 2020:\nPresenting the Stanford Dolman Travel Book of the Year award.\n\nThe Edward Stanford Travel Writing Awards ceremony on 26th February 2020 will be held at The London Transport Museum, in Central London. There will be a Cocktail Reception & Global Food Feast at 7:00pm, followed by the Awards Ceremony. The awards will be hosted by Julia Bradbury.\xa0\nVenue: London Transport Museum, Covent Garden Piazza, London, WC2E 7BB.\nStarts 7:00pm. Dress Code: Smart Casual.\n Tickets available here | More news and events...\n\n\n\nTwitter\n\n\n\nTweets by Benedict Allen\n\nMore tweets\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n"For me personally, exploration isn\'t about conquering nature, planting flags or leaving your mark. It\'s about the opposite: opening yourself up and allowing the place to leave its mark on you..."\n\n\n\n\n\nProudpatron of:\n\nThe TonyTrust\nSavetheRhino\nEnvironmentalJusticeFoundation\n\n\n\xa9 Benedict Allen 2015 \xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 Website by RGP Design\n\n\n\n\n\n\n'